message.content: Ay, listen up, kid. If ya wanna dominate the fantasy football seas this year, you gotta go with my main shrimp, I mean man, Alvin Kamara. This guy's gonna be slicin' through defenses like a katana through a shrimp cocktail. Trust me, he's gonna be the top RB in the game, capisce? But hey, what do I know? I'm just a humble crawfather tryin' to make a splash in the fantasy world.
